headline: PPL Foundation awards grants to 30 nonprofit organizations in eastern and central Pennsylvania
summary: ALLENTOWN - The PPL Foundation this month completed the first of three planned grant programs for 2025, awarding $200,000 in grants to 30 nonprofit organizations working to build stronger communities...
